Jordan Wright has received the largest sum of money from campaign donors

Wright, who has received $59,139, was followed by Maria Ordoñez with nearly $40,000. Shana Harmongoff and Joshua Clennon trailed behind,

receiving just under $14,000 and $12,000, respectively.
